Your project is set up to use **Vite** (a modern build tool), which automatically handles libraries like React. However, your `index.html` currently contains an "Import Map" block that tries to forcefully load React from the internet (CDNs).
These two systems are fighting: Vite tries to load React 18 from your project, and the Import Map tries to load React 19 from the web. This crash results in a white screen.

