You will need to get your configuration values from the Firebase Console (Project Settings -> General -> Your Apps -> SDK Setup and Configuration -> Config).

Go to your **Vercel Dashboard** -> **Settings** -> **Environment Variables** and add these (copy the values from your Firebase console):

